*   ## **_QUEEN OF THE RING ROUND 2: NIA JAX DEF. JADE CARGILL BY DQ_**
    

Jade Cargill has gotten herself disqualified against Nia Jax after Jax insulted Jade to her baby daughter's face. Jade Cargill is out of the tournament.

Nia Jax moves on.

